metadata.name: Searching for my Mind
metadata.description:
In the vastness of space: Extremely energetic cosmic disks that travel through the universe with speeds close to the speed of light annihilate in a matter of seconds the existence of cosmic beings older than some of the oldest constellations and planets in the universe in a apparently static scene but that ends with experiences, memories, abilities... everything; Leaving no trace in the universe.ðŸŒŒ
